title: Suburban Tribe - Elektro 57 (1998)
description:
Suburban Tribe - Elektro 57 / 1998 Spinefarm SPI66CD


Jouni Markkanen - vocals
Roope Siren - guitar
Janne Joutsenniemi - bass
Alec Hirst-Gee - drums
Emerson Burton - keyboard


Suburban Tribe is finnish metal band. (1994-present)

Elektro 57 was their last album with the lead singer Jouni Markkanen.

In the year 2000 he was replaced by Ville Tuomi.


Elektro 57 is exceptional Suburban Tribe album. It has much electronical and industrial, even groovy sounds, unlike other Suburban Tribe's albums.
